    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by. I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a great car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures without breaking the bank, this is the one. It runs smoothly and feels great on the road. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come see it for yourself!",
