    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its structural integrity with a reinforced rear subframe, and the suspension utilizes a calibrated MacPherson strut and multi-link setup for precise lateral grip. Recent service includes a VANOS system refresh and valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain operates with peak volumetric efficiency. A mechanically sound example of BMW's finest naturally aspirated engineering.",
