    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. This beauty has been such a reliable ride for me, and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, clean, and it still drives like a dream. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something dependable that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve priced it to sell, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
