    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically sound, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and includes a documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The factory limited-slip differential provides excellent lock-up, while the suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback and balanced handling characteristic of the M-division's peak era. The exterior shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with spirited use, but the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with no hesitation. Recent maintenance includes a Valve Adjustment and fresh fluids throughout, ensuring this legendary platform is ready for the canyon roads.",
